About Us

We at WeCare provide the best in class home services for all of your needs.

It is a platform to make our urban lives more fulfilling by solving all of our home and personal needs from a single place.

The local service industry is a central part of our lives but us dominated by very few platforms with little competition.

We aim to become the go-to platform for helping customers take care of both their home and personal needs. We want to help you complete projects that are important to you - everything from cleaning and designing your home to taking care of yourself, WeCare has solutions for all!

Our vision is to use technology to structure the highly unorganized services market and to connect our users to the best professionals who can provide all the services they need at a comfortable price.
